name: Google Developer 2025
shortDesc: A global conference for developers to explore the latest Google technologies.
longDesc: Google Developer 2025 is a premier event where developers, engineers, and tech enthusiasts gather to learn about Google's latest innovations in AI, Android, Flutter, Firebase, and more. name: Developer Fest 2025
shortDesc: A tech festival featuring workshops, hackathons, and networking for developers.
